==In media==
*Nick Carraway, the narrator of F. Scott Fitzgerald&#x27;s &quot;The Great Gatsby&quot;, says his family has &quot;a tradition that we&#x27;re descended from the Dukes of Buccleuch&quot;, but then points out that this is not true.

