<doc id="392220" wikidata="Q562473" url="?curid=392220" title="NSZ">
<text>NSZ can refer to:

*Nanking Safety Zone, a demilitarized area in Nanking, China in 1937-1938
*&quot;Narodowe Siły Zbrojne&quot; (National Armed Forces), World War II resistance movement in Poland</text><links>
