<doc id="392253" wikidata="Q815572" url="?curid=392253" title="List of presidents of Guinea">
<text>This article lists the presidents of Guinea, since the country gained independence from France in 1958 (after rejecting to join the French Community in a constitutional referendum).

==Term limits==
As of 2021, there is a two-term limit for the president in the Constitution of Guinea. This limit has been lifted for Conté in 2001 and for Condé in 2020. 

