* Mobius, also known as the Anti-Monitor, a supervillain in DC Comics
* Johann Wilhelm Möbius, a character in the play &quot;The Physicists&quot;
* Moebius, the main antagonistic faction in the video game &quot;Xenoblade Chronicles 3&quot;
